## Store hex digit selection from colorpick into consolidated tr:color storage
## Based on color-step (1-6), maps colorpick (0-15) to hex char and updates storage

# Color step 1 - Red first digit
execute if score @s color-step matches 1 if score @s colorpick matches 0 run data modify storage tr:color d1 set value "0"
